                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17981205-67-victim793 t17981205-67-viclabel355"></join>: Last Saturday was a week, between seven and eight o'clock, I saw the prisoner come into the shop, and put a piece of bacon under her cloak; I called out stop thief; Mary Barrett was shutting the shop window, and she stopped her with the bacon.</p>
